## PopulatableEthersMosaic.unstakeMSIC() method

Withdraw MSIC from staking.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
unstakeMSIC(amount: Decimalish, overrides?: EthersTransactionOverrides): Promise<PopulatedEthersMosaicTransaction<void>>;
```

## Parameters

|  Parameter | Type | Description |
|  --- | --- | --- |
|  amount | [Decimalish](./lib-base.decimalish.md) | Amount of MSIC to withdraw. |
|  overrides | [EthersTransactionOverrides](./lib-ethers.etherstransactionoverrides.md) |  |

## Remarks

As a side-effect, the transaction will also pay out the MSIC stake's [collateral gain](./lib-base.msicstake.collateralgain.md) and [MEUR gain](./lib-base.msicstake.msicgain.md)<!-- -->.
